news.title: Delhi: Cracks in residents' solidarity jeopardise Signature View's redemption
news.para: ​The residents are afraid of just such an eventuality and have been seeking early rehabilitation that will enable them to shift from the building demarcated to be demolished.

news.title: Mumbai: Residents oppose huge PAP project at Kanjurmarg
news.para: The BMC has planned two 23-storey buildings with seven wings to rehabilitate PAPs, including those displaced by the GMLR project.

news.title: Opposition to auction of proposed amenity plots in Pune
news.para: The Hinjewadi Employees and Residents Trust have written to the Pune Metropolitan Development Authority (PMRDA) to stop the auction process.
